sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant G as API Gateway
  participant U as Upstream Contract
  participant B as banking-admin

  C->>G: POST /api/v1/accounts + payload
  G->>G: auth boundary check
  G->>G: resolve correlation id
  G->>U: createAccount(payload, correlation_id)
  U->>B: POST /banking_admin/api/v1/accounts

  alt success
    B-->>U: 201 account payload
    U-->>G: 201 account payload
    G-->>C: 201 passthrough + X-Correlation-ID
  else validation error
    B-->>U: 422 error envelope
    U-->>G: 422 error envelope
    G-->>C: 422 passthrough + X-Correlation-ID
  else upstream unavailable
    U-->>G: transport failure
    G-->>C: 503 upstream_unavailable
  end
